 Task 3 â€“ Combine map(), filter(), reduce()
const scores = [45, 80, 90, 35, 60, 75];
// Filter passing scores (>=50)
// Add 10 bonus marks to each
// Calculate total using reduce()

Code:

const scores = [45, 80, 90, 35, 60, 75];

// Filter passing scores
const passed = scores.filter(s => s >= 50);

// Add 10 bonus marks
const bonusScores = passed.map(s => s + 10);

// Calculate total
const totalScore = bonusScores.reduce((sum, s) => sum + s, 0);

console.log("Passed Scores:", passed);
console.log("After Bonus:", bonusScores);
console.log("Total Score:", totalScore);

Output:-

Passed Scores: [80, 90, 60, 75]
After Bonus: [90, 100, 70, 85]
Total Score: 345

